[BRIDGE]

[Music nearly stops. A single Large Drum beats slowly. The bansuri plays a simple, haunting motif. Acoustic guitar strums sparse, open chords. Jhyaali cymbals produce a soft, sustained shimmer. Vocal is whispered, prayerful.]
[Vocal (gentle, intimate):]
पहाडको चुचुरो, बादल माथि
त्यो ठाउँ जहाँ उज्यालो जम्दछ
भेटिने सबै भाइबहिनीहरू
झगडा पनि समयसँगै मेल खान्छ
अब डगमगाउँदिन

[The frame drum begins a slow, steady pulse. Jhyaali resumes delicate rhythm. The flute melody gradually builds in intensity.]

[FINAL CHORUS – KEY CHANGE]

[The song modulates up to F Major. Every element enters at maximum intensity. Electric guitars are wall-of-sound huge. Flute plays a rapid, celebratory solo over the top. Large Drum and Damphu create a thunderous groove. Jhyaali cymbals sparkle continuously. Strings sweep dramatically. Vocal is at its most powerful, layered in rich harmonies. This is the climatic high point.]
[Vocal (epic, triumphant, unifying):]
नयाँ भोरतिर हात फैलाउँछु
प्रार्थनाको स्वर आकाशमा नाच्छ
सिंहराजाको बाटो, बाँदरराजाको सपना
बुद्धको दया हृदयमा समेटेँ

गर्वका साथ यो हातमा उत्कीर्ण गर्छु
अहिले, म उड्छु

[OUTRO]

[All instruments fade except for the flute, which plays the main melody one last time. A final Large Drum hit echoes once. Wind and distant chimes return. A soft ambient synth pad sustains under the flute.]
[Vocal (soft, fading):]
la la la… उज्यालोको परे
la la la… धडकन गुन्जन्छ

[Final flute note lingers, then silence.]

[Whispered, fading:]
सदैव… संगै